                         Privacy and Security Notice

   BNL provides infrastructure support to the Department of Energy (DOE)
   Atmospheric Radiation Measurement (ARM) program.

        * ARM Databases maintained by BNL:
           [blue.gif] PIF/CAR/DQR Data Base
               [blue.gif] Publication Data Base
               [blue.gif] SGP Meta Data System

        * BNL also provides support for ARM in the following area(s):
           [blue.gif] External Data Center

        * BNL's General ARM Documentation

   Contact Richard Wagener for additional information on work done by BNL in
   support of ARM.
